      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FURIOUS FALCON (3) missed the frame last time when fourth (24.17) at Traralgon in a Grade 5 but not beaten far the start prior. Will find this more suitable and can atone. MAD HATTER ROSE (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.75 lengths at Warragul in a handy 22.83 beating Akina Johnny. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Should be in this for a long way. PAW ALLESANDRA (1) has been out of the placings last couple but impressed when clocking a 22.23 over 390m at Shepparton three starts back. Top win three back and rates a key player again. PAW HAZELTON (6) warrants respect although new to this track.",
